## Gating
You may emit <conclusion> ONLY after: (a) at least one pytest run produced a
runtime failure, AND (b) you have driven a stateful PDB session past a real
(non-pdb-internal) stop frame for at least 3 commands. The system rejects
premature conclusions and asks you to drive PDB further.

